snippet: Russia called on Ukraine's authorities and rebels on Saturday to give international experts access to the crash site of a Malaysian Airlines plane, the foreign ministry said....

headline.print_headline: Russia Calls on Kiev, Rebels to Help Experts at Plane Crash Site
headline.main: Russia Calls on Kiev, Rebels to Help Experts at Plane Crash Site

lead_paragraph: Russia called on Ukraine's authorities and rebels on Saturday to give international experts access to the crash site of a Malaysian Airlines plane, the foreign ministry said.
